..TEXT:
|Proemio.~  ^Incipit XVIIII' cantus prime cantice
Comedie.~  In isto XVIIII+o~ cantu autor tractat de tertia
malabulgia, que incipit ibi:
..TEXT:
<<<FORMATTING-OFF>>>
     Gi@a eravamo, a la seguente tomba,
..TEXT:
<<<FORMATTING-OFF>>>
                        (^Inf.~ XIX. )
..TEXT:
et finit ibi:
..TEXT:
<<<FORMATTING-OFF>>>
     rimont@o per la via onde discese.
..TEXT:
<<<FORMATTING-OFF>>>
                        (^Inf.~ XIX. 26)
..TEXT:
Ponit autem in ista bulgia symoniacos, pena quorum est
quod sunt deorsum capite supplantati, et plantas habent velut
candelas accensas.
..TEXT:
In isto XVIIII+o~ cantu continentur quatuor comparationes
{*vv. 16-18; 28-30; 49-51; 58-60*} et totidem notabilia {*vv.
37-39; 90-96; 100-105; 115-117*} et tria vaticinia {*vv. 79-81;
82-84; 85-87*}.
..TCHR:
